<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.6.5">
<l>muṉnara ciṅkama tākiya vuṇaṉ</l>
<l rend="indent">mukkiyat taimuṭip pāṉmū vulakil</l>
<l>maṉṉarañ cummatu cūtaṉaṉ vāyil</l>
<l rend="indent">kuḻaliṉō caicevi yaippaṟṟi vāṅka</l>
<l>naṉṉaram puṭaiya tumpuru vōṭu</l>
<l rend="indent">nārata ṉumtamtam vīṇaima ṟantu</l>
<l>kiṉṉa ramitu ṉaṅkaḷum tamtam</l>
<l rend="indent">kiṉṉaram toṭuki lōmeṉṟa ṉarē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When the music of the flute at the mouth of Madhusūdana,</l>
<l rend="indent">who terrified the kings of the three worlds</l>
<l rend="indent">when, as a man-lion long ago,</l>
<l rend="indent">[he] destroyed the superiority of the Asura,</l>
<l>grasped and carried away the ears of Tumburu and Nārada,</l>
<l rend="indent">with good stringed instruments,</l>
<l>they disregarded their vīṇās, and the Kiṉṉara couples declared,</l>
<l>“We cannot touch our lutes!”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
